name: Cryptorg
public_notice: Cryptorg has migrated from their old contract to a new one. For more information, please visit this post.
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
Automated Digital Currency Trading

The service is designed to automate trade on various cryptocurrency exchanges. User-friendly interface for creating and configuring trading bots. Service is available 24/7/365. Customize notifications via Telegram, group chat and many other buns.
